[[File:Clawthorn.jpg|thumb|right|250px|A clawthorn on Yavin 4.]]
The '''clawthorn''' was a scrubby plant with large hook-shaped thorns, found on the moon [[Yavin 4/Legends|Yavin 4]].<ref name="CotF">''[[Champions of the Force]]''</ref> Like [[raventhorn plant]]s, clawthorns could be found in many rocky mountainous region of Yavin 4.<ref name="SWG">{{GalaxiesAED}}</ref>

